item.description:
Denis Goddard has put together an audio CD of clips from Free Talk Live (and one from Stefan Molyneux) personalized for high school students, and has purchased 2500 copies. It's up to us to get them out to the people.

Project website: http://freestateblogs...

I'm committing myself to a schedule for next week - one school per day, at closing time. I could really use some help to hand them out and company for moral support. Should only take about 20 minutes. You can meet me there, or contact me to make plans to meet before and go together.

For liberty!

(BTW-I'm creating a separate event for each of the five days.)
item.name: FTL4HS CD hand-outs
